										<h3>OpenTTD Installer</h3>
									</header>
									<p><a href="http://www.openttd.org/" icon="popup" target="_blank">OpenTTD</a> is an open source clone of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transport_Tycoon" icon="popup" target="_blank">Transport Tycoon Deluxe</a>, and I am the original author of the installer for the Windows version of OpenTTD.  This installer is written using <a href="http://nsis.sourceforge.net/" icon="popup" target="_blank">NSIS</a> and still includes some of my original code, including the Welcome dialog that pops up when you upgrade from one version to another.</p>
